The paper discusses the use of neural networks and decision-making tools, which are commonly studied in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), control systems (cs.SY), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). The focus on interpretability and safety of machine learning models suggests a stronger association with cs.LG and cs.AI.
